{
  "stem": "25651.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this was the colonel that was going to start a kibbutz in Israel, or Palestine then.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they decided one of the leaders-- there were two leaders who shared the national leadership-- Fredy Hirsch and my brother, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they had to decide who will go to Palestine and who will lead the movement in-- in occupied Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they did it by drawing the matches.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They broke a match.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And whoever got the broken match stayed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my brother got the-- he chose the right match.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he was the leader of the [HEBREW] that went to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he went to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember in '39 coming-- we were still able to travel-- although the Germans were already in occupation of Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We came to Prague with my mother and with [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we said goodbye to [NON-ENGLISH] when he departed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He already was then engaged to [NON-ENGLISH], who became his wife.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] is quite amusing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She wanted to leave Czechoslovakia because of-- she saw what was happening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was a young woman of our town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She wasn't in the youth movement at all, and the only way to leave was through the youth movement.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she came to the headquarters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she said, well, who is in charge here of this group that's going?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they said, well--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[POINTING] --she want to see [NON-ENGLISH] Honigwachs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she says, well, I saw [NON-ENGLISH] Honigwachs, and I made eyes with him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I became his girlfriend, and that's how I got to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, ask me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember almost everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I could probably tell you--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--sometimes day by day happenings.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
